nodes.text: Liz Wilson (born Friday Wilson on November 29, 1979) portrayed the handmaiden Eirtaé in Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace. She was credited as "Friday 'Liz' Wilson" in the movie.
In 1995, Wilson also appeared in the direct-to-video film Life 101.
